s2.note:
This section is meant to become a set of guidelines for all &xslt4j;
committers and developers who wish to submit patches.  It's still in progress; 
suggestions to xalan-dev@xml.apache.org appreciated.

ul.li:
Major version releases: when significant new or changed functionality comes out, 
we bump up the major build number; i.e. from 2.3 to 3.0.  This is fairly rare; 
anyone reading xalan-dev will know when this is happening.

s3.p:
&xslt4j; includes a number of XML source files, XSL stylesheets, document type definition (DTD)
      files, entity relationship (ENT) files, graphics, and a JavaScript file that provide the input for the &xslt4j;
      HTML User's Guide, and the overview and package-level documents used during the generation of Javadoc.
